%p
  = "Dear #{@resource.first_name} #{@resource.last_name},".titleize
%p
  Your account has been locked due to an excessive number of unsuccessful sign-in attempts. You can unlock your account by clicking the link below which will take you to the sign-in page.
%p
  = link_to 'Unlock my account', unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token)
%p
  If you have lost your password, then click the link 'Forgot your password?' on the sign-in page to receive an email with instructions to set a new password.

%p
  Yours sincerely,
%p
  Crime Case Management Team
  %br
  %b
    Legal Aid Agency
